{"tid":1207419,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"在場first aid,有少少野想提下大家","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:34:03.000Z","uid":144871,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46a2220f756289c2900a80357b8633cae3321a62","tid":1207419,"uid":144871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"知我係邊個嘅你，無謂爆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經返左屋企補眠<br />\n<br />\n我11號20:00就已經到現場<br />\nWalk in 同現場師兄組成first aid team<br />\n係現場stand by , 直到12號08:00<br />\n（即今朝開始衝龍和道）<br />\n<br />\n傷者就直線上升<br />\n<br />\n講下如果你想去，或者係想幫手補給<br />\n（我只講急救所需要的，其他一律不提）<br />\n你可以買/唔好買咩<br />\n<br />\n1:<br />\n請買大塊少少嘅膠布，唔係買痴手指個種<br />\n<br />\n2:<br />\n如要應付「食椒」，請買「生理鹽水」<br />\n桃紅色嘅消毒藥水，只會用黎洗傷口<br />\n對處理食椒，係需要大量生理鹽水<br />\n<br />\n3:<br />\n請大家最低限度，帶備自己食用嘅糧食&amp;飲用水<br />\n你有手/有人幫，先考慮買更多物資<br />\n<br />\n4:<br />\n請大家食夠訓夠，係屋企去晒大小<br />\n先好出黎長期作戰<br />\n衝出去個下，有人搬搬下鐵馬就暈咗<br />\n同我講未食早餐，有個仲話三日無訓過<br />\n<br />\n5:<br />\n搬任何野都要小心<br />\n有大多損傷都係搬動鐵器而造成<br />\n睇住有破傷風<br />\n<br />\n6:<br />\n頂唔住嘅你，唔舒服唔洗覺得唔好意思<br />\n大叫first aid ，兩隻手做十字<br />\n然後傳話嘅人請盡量指出準確位置<br />\nFirst aid team 係非常願意跑過黎協助大家<br />\n<br />\n我有病在身，陣中仲落雨<br />\n頂唔順了，直接退下火線<br />\n要停了"},{"pid":"b487ed56d98d62860f8fcc7992ac932b577f509c","tid":1207419,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"救護兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡力而為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有成班頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e64bff9edb3a716da38fa6edc42832c5f18f18a","tid":1207419,"uid":19285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"感激！"},{"pid":"22199475957f12a7bbf72f57ffe42a71f552ef10","tid":1207419,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"推 更加多人要有急救知識"},{"pid":"9989ed384b637198850cd62f617e7913c3391274","tid":1207419,"uid":133649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"有basic first aid牌夠唔夠do"},{"pid":"5f10d9728fd7e7d65115a85c591e8c843a9190d3","tid":1207419,"uid":220947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}